/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw第九名個風名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n／"},{"pid":"75a0c538fa376909c80162599d5ac3fb64a28390","tid":355791,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ft58yu3z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fft58yu3z&h=41b73d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m819bx3e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm819bx3e&h=a66b90c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港天文台排奧鹿第三，韋恩第二，<br />\n日本排奧鹿第二，韋因第四<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw第九名個風名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n JMA既紀錄都有分兩種，一種係好似數字颱風網既計法，唔計入中間TD階段既時間，另一種係JMA官網上面公佈既計法，包括埋中間TD階段既時間。如果按照後者既紀錄，韋恩係第一，奧鹿係第三。"},{"pid":"3bf8b25358eae549c8354203f4a1fc8b52bfa732","tid":355791,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T17:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ft58yu3z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fft58yu3z&h=41b73d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m819bx3e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm819bx3e&h=a66b90c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港天文台排奧鹿第三，韋恩第二，<br />\n日本排奧鹿第二，韋恩第四<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw第九名個風名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n JMA既紀錄都有分兩種，一種係好似數字颱風網既計法，唔計入中間TD階段既時間，另一種係JMA官網上面公佈既計法，包括埋中間TD階段既時間。如果按照後者既紀錄，韋恩係第一，奧鹿係第三。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係同hko一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一或hko其實就係直接引用jma官網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf13b8264a641845744159e3b4ed1705c10c3b9","tid":355791,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T17:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5847ae1abc08e2623b8250e7d1ba5d094951f7","tid":355791,"uid":120791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ft58yu3z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fft58yu3z&h=41b73d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m819bx3e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm819bx3e&h=a66b90c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港天文台排奧鹿第三，韋恩第二，<br />\n日本排奧鹿第二，韋因第四<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw第九名個風名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n JMA既紀錄都有分兩種，一種係好似數字颱風網既計法，唔計入中間TD階段既時間，另一種係JMA官網上面公佈既計法，包括埋中間TD階段既時間。如果按照後者既紀錄，韋恩係第一，奧鹿係第三。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n颱風麗妲是1972年太平洋颱風季最強的熱帶氣旋，也是自有氣象記錄以来第一個也是目前為止唯一一個正面登陸天津的熱帶氣旋，同時還是當時西北太平洋維持時間最長的熱帶氣旋。<br />\n<br />\n最後，麗妲在7月27日上午於天津塘沽登陸，然後橫過北京，成為有記錄以來唯一一個在天津登陸和橫過北京的颱風。麗妲登陸後減弱較為緩慢，並一直向西北移動，到蒙古高原附近才最終完全消散。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cf/Rita_1972_track.png/300px-Rita_1972_track.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fcf%2FRita_1972_track.png%2F300px-Rita_1972_track.png&h=12a9cbf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0361eedc0b2c6798d4b5e7679155ca3f103aa1c","tid":355791,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:17:10.000Z","msg":"當時大氣咩環境，令到佢可以係華北內陸咁耐時間？"},{"pid":"ecf63f9e0309ee2a91f0bb4b417ebef700fcd18a","tid":355791,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:19:09.000Z","msg":"香港嘅風名又用咗喺遠洋風度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8583f95489b080732244bfc98bb9e36d48aa7d","tid":355791,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:33:48.000Z","msg":"又高偉又極內陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc971132230a4a7ef9272ca363140468cbdd390","tid":355791,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T22:30:43.000Z","msg":"冇雷公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb14ca7618bd6f00a5f835ba424adb613e0b21b","tid":355791,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T23:13:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ft58yu3z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fft58yu3z&h=41b73d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m819bx3e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm819bx3e&h=a66b90c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港天文台排奧鹿第三，韋恩第二，<br />\n日本排奧鹿第二，韋因第四<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw第九名個風名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n JMA既紀錄